187
00:12:34,900 --> 00:12:36,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Kashiwagi!</font>

188
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a while.</font>

189
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:39,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

190
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:42,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was talking to Kuroda about 
