191
00:12:42,660 --> 00:12:44,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys wanna join?</font>

192
00:12:45,830 --> 00:12:46,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds good.</font>

193
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where at?</font>

194
00:12:49,340 --> 00:12:50,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Of course...</i></font>

195
00:12:50,910 --> 00:12:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why did I expect that he meant 
