198
00:13:01,340 --> 00:13:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with that?</font>

199
00:13:03,560 --> 00:13:04,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

200
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kashiwagi makes me smile.</i></font>

201
00:13:09,820 --> 00:13:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But also hurts me a bit.</i></font>

202
00:13:12,820 --> 00:13:17,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should have just been friends 
with Kizuki, too.</font>

203
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My only choice was to 
stay with him as a friend.</i></font>

204
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#f8f5e1"><font face="Times New Roman">To-ou Medical University Hospital</font></font></font>

205
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#ebeedb"><font face="Times New Roman">To-ou Medical University Hospital</font></font></font>

206
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:37,150
