214
00:14:04,070 --> 00:14:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for the meal!</font>

215
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:14,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm fine as long as I can 
