216
00:14:14,710 --> 00:14:16,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's what I thought.</i></font>

217
00:14:19,990 --> 00:14:23,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go to the same high school... 
Let's go to the same high school...</font>

