00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:39,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You aren't studying at all!</font>

226
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well...</font>

227
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shin's notes are too advanced.</font>

228
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:49,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That guy's too smart.</font>

229
00:14:49,370 --> 00:14:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at this!</font>

230
00:14:49,370 --> 00:14:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font size="28"><font color="#6a6968">Exam Prep Notes for Clowns</font></font></font>

231
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:54,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hmm...</font>

