00:14:54,620 --> 00:14:57,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Best of luck on your studies, Mizuho.</font>

233
00:14:57,780 --> 00:14:59,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go to the same high school.</font>

