00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quite the crowd here.</font>

245
00:15:36,920 --> 00:15:38,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo!</font>

246
00:15:38,460 --> 00:15:40,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you bored seeing this every day?</font>

247
00:15:40,170 --> 00:15:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Saito-senpai is so cool!</font>

248
00:15:43,530 --> 00:15:46,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's handsome and super fast...</font>

249
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

250
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:52,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki! Don't lose!</font>

251
00:15:55,770 --> 00:15:58,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't know yourself the most.</font>

252
00:15:58,910 --> 00:15:59,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

253
00:16:00,830 --> 00:16:02,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

254
00:16:18,530 --> 00:16:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But because he's scared,</i></font>

255
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he's hiding his true feelings...</i></font>

256
00:16:28,550 --> 00:16:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He'll definitely regret
 it when he's older.</i></font>

257
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:44,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a nice song, Shiraishi-chan.</font>

258
00:16:44,460 --> 00:16:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's it called?</font>

259
00:16:47,820 --> 00:16:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And she's ignoring me.</font>

