00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:51,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiraishi-chan.</font>

261
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:54,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to call me "Shiraishi-sensei."</font>

262
00:16:56,490 --> 00:16:59,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I gather up some courage...</font>

263
00:16:59,450 --> 00:17:00,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and get rejected...</font>

264
00:17:01,550 --> 00:17:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you cheer me up?</font>

265
00:17:07,050 --> 00:17:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably not.</font>

266
00:17:08,670 --> 00:17:12,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I could play you this song.</font>

267
00:17:24,780 --> 00:17:26,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hoshikawa-kun.</font>

268
00:17:26,540 --> 00:17:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The name of this song is...</font>

269
00:17:37,370 --> 00:17:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30">2024</font></font>

270
00:17:37,900 --> 00:17:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I decided that I'd be by her side 
no matter what happens.</font>

271
00:17:43,370 --> 00:17:46,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an7}<font color="#d5d6d9">Manga Seminar
 <font color="#be7784">Let's Draw Manga</font></font></b></font>

272
00:17:48,060 --> 00:17:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Greetings. Pizza delivery.</font>

273
00:17:51,230 --> 00:17:52,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo!</font>

274
00:17:52,870 --> 00:17:57,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard from your dad 
that you're not doing well?</font>

275
00:17:58,410 --> 00:18:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you going to do with those?</font>

276
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, well...</font>

277
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:05,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm thinking of giving up on making manga.</font>

278
00:18:05,850 --> 00:18:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You serious?</font>

279
00:18:06,990 --> 00:18:07,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

280
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone else is busy 
 job searching...</font>

281
00:18:11,710 --> 00:18:14,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I haven't even debuted.</font>

282
00:18:15,140 --> 00:18:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I tried to do my best like Kizuki.</font>

283
00:18:18,380 --> 00:18:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's giving it his all to represent Japan.</font>

284
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it feels like I'm 
still clinging to a dream</font>

285
00:18:24,110 --> 00:18:25,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that will never come true.</font>

286
00:18:26,510 --> 00:18:29,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must look so childish to you, Syugo.</font>

287
00:18:30,130 --> 00:18:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's what you've 
been wanting to do, right?</font>

288
00:18:35,820 --> 00:18:37,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now...</font>

289
00:18:37,280 --> 00:18:40,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what I write, 
it doesn't feel right.</font>

290
00:18:40,930 --> 00:18:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know if this is what 
I really want to do anymore.</font>

291
00:18:44,710 --> 00:18:45,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't draw anything.</font>

292
00:18:49,510 --> 00:18:50,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why...</font>

293
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:52,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to start job searching!</font>

