<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're forcing that smile.</font>

295
00:19:00,250 --> 00:19:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo?</font>

296
00:19:03,330 --> 00:19:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here. For your new resolve!</font>

297
00:19:05,360 --> 00:19:06,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

298
00:19:07,490 --> 00:19:08,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nice.</font>

299
00:19:08,850 --> 00:19:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that's what you decided on,</font>

300
00:19:11,670 --> 00:19:14,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">go on and do that!</font>

301
00:19:16,060 --> 00:19:17,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

302
00:19:17,930 --> 00:19:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="30">2028</font></font>

303
00:19:23,790 --> 00:19:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did he leave me?</font>

304
00:19:37,850 --> 00:19:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm borrowing your kitchen.</font>

305
00:19:39,950 --> 00:19:41,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eat whatever you'd like.</font>

306
00:19:42,130 --> 00:19:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And take a break from work, too.</font>

307
00:19:44,140 --> 00:19:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't even think about Kizuki today.</font>

308
00:19:52,210 --> 00:19:54,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon, you have to eat something, Mizuho.</font>

309
00:19:54,850 --> 00:19:57,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please. Just one bite.</font>

310
00:20:09,790 --> 00:20:10,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo...</font>

311
00:20:12,930 --> 00:20:14,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so good.</font>

312
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho...</font>

313
00:20:19,100 --> 00:20:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Syugo.</font>

314
00:20:23,150 --> 00:20:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For always cheering me up.</font>

315
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:37,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop grinning at me 
like that while eating.</font>

316
00:20:38,170 --> 00:20:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help it. It's good.</font>

317
00:20:42,790 --> 00:20:43,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo?</font>

318
00:20:44,580 --> 00:20:46,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

319
00:20:46,470 --> 00:20:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You always make a scary face, Syugo.</font>

320
00:20:49,760 --> 00:20:53,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was so shocked 
when you jumped at Kizuki.</font>

321
00:20:53,340 --> 00:20:56,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't seen you make 
a face like that before.</font>

322
00:20:57,900 --> 00:21:00,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a chef, what would you do 
if you hurt your hand?</font>

323
00:21:01,330 --> 00:21:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you out of your mind?</font>

324
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You and Kizuki!</font>

325
