<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Throwing hands at each other like thatâ€”</font>

326
00:21:08,210 --> 00:21:12,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No more talking about Kizuki.</font>

327
00:21:15,670 --> 00:21:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo?</font>

328
00:21:18,420 --> 00:21:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now...</font>

329
00:21:19,790 --> 00:21:21,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The person in front of you...</font>

330
00:21:23,990 --> 00:21:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is me.</font>

331
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:35,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Out of anyone else, 
the one by your side...</font>

332
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:40,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is me.</font>

333
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:25,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo?</font>

334
00:23:27,750 --> 00:23:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?</i></font>

335
00:23:34,080 --> 00:23:35,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time to go.</font>

336
00:23:35,990 --> 00:23:37,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll drop you off.</font>

337
00:23:40,010 --> 00:23:42,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to chaperon me.</font>

338
00:23:54,760 --> 00:23:56,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The name of this song is...</i></font>

339
00:23:57,540 --> 00:23:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"My Regretful Heart."</i></font>

